{"title":"Books That Changed My Perspective","type":"page","uid":"b1295aa3d4127d29c4985f9da2d27a5d","text":" My Essential Reading The books that shaped my thinking and continue to inspire me 图解大模型：生成式AI原理与实战 Jay Alammar & Maarten Grootendorst 这本书图文...","date":"2025-08-27T11:41:26.000Z","updated":"2025-08-27T14:57:57.356Z","comments":true,"path":"api/pages/books/index.json","covers":[],"excerpt":"","content":"<div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n  <h1 style=\"font-size: 2.5em; color: #6200ea; margin-bottom: 10px;\">My Essential Reading</h1>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em; color: #666; font-style: italic;\">The books that shaped my thinking and continue to inspire me</p>\n  <hr style=\"width: 80px; margin: 20px auto; border-top: 2px solid #6200ea;\">\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background-color: rgba(98, 0, 234, 0.05); border-radius: 12px; padding: 25px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(98, 0, 234, 0.15); margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n  <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; flex-wrap: wrap;\">\n    <div style=\"flex: 0 0 180px; margin-right: 25px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n      <img src=\"/books/book_cover/hands_on_LLM.jpg\" alt=\"Hands-On Large Language Models\" style=\"width: 100%; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\">\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; min-width: 280px;\">\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 0; color: #6200ea; font-size: 1.6em;\">图解大模型：生成式AI原理与实战</h2>\n      <p style=\"color: #666; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 15px;\">Jay Alammar & Maarten Grootendorst</p>\n      <div style=\"width: 50px; height: 3px; background-color: #6200ea; margin-bottom: 15px;\"></div>\n      <p style=\"line-height: 1.6; color: #fff;\">这本书图文并茂，由浅入深地介绍了大语言模型的工作原理和应用方法。不仅包含理论知识，还提供了实战代码，是入门生成式AI的绝佳选择。</p>\n      <p style=\"line-height: 1.6; color: #fff;\">书中的可视化解释让复杂的概念变得易于理解，适合各个水平的读者。通过实践项目，读者可以亲手构建和优化自己的AI模型，真正掌握这一前沿技术。</p>\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 20px; padding: 15px; background-color: rgba(98, 0, 234, 0.08); border-left: 4px solid #6200ea; border-radius: 4px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0; font-style: italic; color: #fff;\">\"理解大模型不仅是技术问题，更是思维方式的转变。\"</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background-color: rgba(98, 0, 234, 0.05); border-radius: 12px; padding: 25px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(98, 0, 234, 0.15); margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n  <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; flex-wrap: wrap;\">\n    <div style=\"flex: 0 0 180px; margin-right: 25px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n      <img src=\"/books/book_cover/principles.png\" alt=\"Principles by Ray Dalio\" style=\"width: 100%; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\">\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; min-width: 280px;\">\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 0; color: #6200ea; font-size: 1.6em;\">原则</h2>\n      <p style=\"color: #666; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 15px;\">Ray Dalio</p>\n      <div style=\"width: 50px; height: 3px; background-color: #6200ea; margin-bottom: 15px;\"></div>\n      <p style=\"line-height: 1.6; color: #fff;\">桥水基金创始人Ray Dalio分享了他的生活和工作原则，这些原则帮助他建立了世界上最成功的对冲基金之一。这本书提供了一个系统化思考问题和做决策的框架，教导我们如何在复杂多变的环境中创造出独特完美的自我。</p>\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 20px;\">\n        <div style=\"padding: 15px; background-color: rgba(98, 0, 234, 0.08); border-left: 4px solid #6200ea; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">\n          <p style=\"margin: 0; font-style: italic; color: #fff;\">\"痛苦 + 反思 = 进步\"</p>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"padding: 15px; background-color: rgba(98, 0, 234, 0.08); border-left: 4px solid #6200ea; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">\n          <p style=\"margin: 0; font-style: italic; color: #fff;\">\"拥抱现实，应对现实。\"</p>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"padding: 15px; background-color: rgba(98, 0, 234, 0.08); border-left: 4px solid #6200ea; border-radius: 4px;\">\n          <p style=\"margin: 0; font-style: italic; color: #fff;\">\"用可信度加权的决策方式比简单地听从自己或他人的意见要好得多。\"</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 50px; padding: 30px; background-color: rgba(98, 0, 234, 0.05); border-radius: 12px;\">\n  <p style=\"font-style: italic; color: #fff;\">有好书推荐？欢迎在<a href=\"/page/message-board\" style=\"color: #6200ea; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px dotted #6200ea;\">留言板</a>分享你的想法！</p>\n</div>","count_time":{"symbolsCount":752,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\"><span class=\"toc-text\">My Essential Reading</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\"><span class=\"toc-text\">图解大模型：生成式AI原理与实战</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\"><span class=\"toc-text\">原则</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","data":[]}